::DarkMouse::

She keeps going and stops at a clearing at the base of the mountain.  She 
looks around for the object that was glittering earlier.  She frowns as she 
discovers what was glittering was a large water spring bubbling up.

"BLAST!"
She was disapointed in herself.  She thought she had found something.  She 
plodded long near the spring.
"Of alll the rotton luck."
She just keep looking about for something, but nothing turned up.
She was about to give up.  All she saw was rock with lots of weeds and 
floliage growing on it.
"Megatron will slag me for letting him down."
She leaned up against the rock face.  It gave way and she fell backward into 
a hugh cave. "WHOAH!"  She landed on her backside with a thud.
"Holy Cybertron."
The cave was huge.  It was at least 300 feet tot he ceiling and had a huge 
hole in the top that let in light.  She wakled back intot he cave and found 
many natural chambers in it.
"YAHOO!  I DID IT!"
She turned on her commlink. "Megaton, Mission accomplished.  Returning back 
to base."
She ran out of the cave, stood infrontof it to mark the quardinates and ran 
back as fast as she could to let Megatron know what she had found.
